%20the%20level%20playing%20field%20vis-a-vis%20the%20political%20functionaries%20of%20other%20parties%20and%20candidates.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20photographs%20of%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Chief%20Ministers%2C%20Ministers%20and%20other%20political%20functionaries%20should%20not%20be%20displayed%2C%20this%20instruction%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20applicable%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20images%20of%20national%20leaders%2C%20poets%2C%20and%20prominent%20historical%20personalities%20of%20the%20past%2C%20and%20the%20President%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Governors.%C2%A0%20In%20case%20of%20any%20doubt%20in%20this%20regard%20regarding%20removal%20of%20any%20photograph%20or%20images%2C%20the%20issue%20may%20be%20referred%20to%20the%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%20of%20the%20State%2F%20Union%20Territory%20concerned%20before%20taking%20action%20in%20the%20matter%20%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20other%20state%20government%20websites%20have%20now%20removed%20photographs%20of%20the%20chief%20ministers%20from%20their%20state%20websites.%20This%20move%20to%20curtail%20influence%20on%20voters%20online%20provides%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20opposition%20parties.%20With%20the%20enforcement%20of%20MCC%20in%20cyberspace%2C%20ECI%20is%20taking%20a%20stance%20against%20the%20usage%20of%20undue%20influence%20on%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21171511%2FScreenshot-2024-03-21-at-5.14.53-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21171511%2FScreenshot-2024-03-21-at-5.14.53-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3