dic%20Body%20Pillow%20is%20the%20firmest%20we%20tested%2C%20which%20is%20ideal%20for%20those%20recovering%20from%20injuries%20or%20back%20pain.%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Hernandez%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tempur-Pedic%20is%20much%20firmer%20than%20the%20other%20pillows%20I%20tested.%20While%20this%20is%20a%20great%20feature%20for%20larger%20individuals%20and%20people%20looking%20for%20extra%20support%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20as%20comfortable%20for%20smaller%20folks%20or%20people%20who%20prefer%20a%20softer%20pillow.%20The%20foam%20is%20dense%20and%20heavy%2C%20so%20moving%20it%20around%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20could%20be%20tiring%20for%20people%20recovering%20from%20injuries%2C%20though%20the%20added%20heft%20means%20it%20doesn't%20fall%20off%20or%20move%20around%20the%20bed%20as%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EBest%20cooling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Zoma%20Sleep%20Body%20Pillow%20is%20made%20with%20high-quality%20materials%20that%20kept%20me%20cool%20and%20comfortable%20throughout%20the%20night.%20The%20cover%20is%20made%20from%20a%20blend%20of%20stretchy%2C%20lightweight%20polyester%20and%20spandex.%20It's%20filled%20with%20shredded%20gel%20memory%20foam%20intended%20to%20keep%20hot%20sleepers%20at%20a%20comfortable%20temperature.%20It's%20a%20very%20well-made%2C%20high-quality%20body%20pillow%20that%20provides%20great%20support%20and%20breathability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20somewhat%20firmer%20than%20the%20Coop%20pillow%20but%20still%20provides%20great%20support%20and%20comfort.%20The%206-inch%20loft%20is%20helpful%20for%20side%20sleepers%20like%20me%20who%20need%20support%20between%20the%20knees.%20After%20a%20few%20nights%20of%20sleeping%20with%20the%20Zoma%2C%20I%20noticed%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20my%20posture%20and%20spinal%20alignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Zoma%20pillow%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20paisley%20print%20sheet%2C%20in%20its%20original%20packaging.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608c1c1534af8d001859a27d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZoma%20makes%20an%20exceptional%20cooling%20body%20pillow%20that%20is%20great%20for%20hot%20sleepers.%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Hernandez%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Zoma%20Sleep%20is%202%20inches%20shorter%20than%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20possible%20to%20rest%20my%20head%20on%20it%20and%20have%20full%20leg%20support%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20I'm%20relatively%20short%2C%20so%20this%20could%20be%20a%20more%20noticeable%20issue%20for%20taller%20folks%20who%20want%20a%20pillow%20that%20supports%20the%20whole%20body.%20The%20smaller%20size%20could%20be%20perfect%20for%20those%20who%20sleep%20with%20a%20partner%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20hog%20the%20whole%20bed.%20The%20cover%20is%20also%20not%20removable%2C%20which%20makes%20washing%20and%20drying%20the%20pillow%20a%20lengthy%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20shorter%20size%20and%20complicated%20washing%20process%2C%20the%20Zoma%20does%20provide%20excellent%20body%20support%20and%20absorbs%20heat%20well.%20For%20pregnant%20people%2C%20this%20pillow%20is%20firm%20enough%20to%20rest%20a%20growing%20belly%20on%20to%20relieve%20pressure%20on%20the%20shoulders%20and%20hips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EMost%20innovative%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20particularly%20excited%20to%20review%20the%20Buffy%20Wiggle%20pillow%2C%20and%20it%20did%20not%20disappoint.%20The%20pillow%20has%20a%20white%20cover%20shell%20crafted%20from%20100%25%20fiber%20derived%20from%20eucalyptus.%20This%20fabric%20requires%20less%20water%20to%20produce%20than%20conventional%20cotton%2C%20it's%20also%20biodegradable%20and%20compostable.%20Mine%20got%20softer%20after%20the%20first%20wash.%20You%20can%20also%20choose%20from%2011%20pillowcase%20colors%2C%20including%20linen%20and%20fleece%2C%20purchased%20se