tion%20to%20sustainability.%20With%20its%20innovative%20features%20and%20commitment%20to%20environmental%20responsibility%2C%20that's%20why%20it's%20our%20top%20choice%20for%20the%20most%20innovative%20category%20in%20this%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EBest%20for%20pregnancy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20tested%20the%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20Side%20Sleeper%20Pillow%20for%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pillow-for-side-sleepers%5C%22%3Ebest%20pillow%20for%20side%20sleepers%3C%2Fa%3E%20guide%2C%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20materials%20and%20effectiveness%20at%20offering%20relief%20for%20neck%20and%20back%20pain.%20With%20sleep%20solutions%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20brand%2C%20the%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20Memory%20Foam%20Pregnancy%20Body%20Pillow%20was%20designed%20with%20expecting%20mothers%20in%20mind%20to%20address%20their%20unique%20needs%20throughout%20all%20stages%20of%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20portion%20of%20testing%2C%20I%20had%20my%20sister-in-law%2C%20who%20is%20in%20her%20third%20trimester%2C%20try%20it.%20She%20mentioned%20needing%20proper%20head%2C%20back%2C%20hip%2C%20and%20knee%20support%20while%20sleeping.%20She%20said%20the%20Eli%20%26amp%3B%20Elm%20allowed%20her%20to%20rest%20in%20different%20positions%20comfortably%20while%20minimizing%20pressure%20on%20her%20joints%20and%20improving%20her%20overall%20sleep%20quality.%20The%20ergonomic%20%26quot%3BJ%26quot%3B%20shape%20won%20her%20over%2C%20and%20she%20plans%20to%20continue%20using%20it%20post-pregnancy.%20Plus%2C%20the%20removable%20and%20easy-to-wash%20pillowcase%20was%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20her%20maintenance%20routine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22eli%20and%20elm%20pregnancy%20pillow%20on%20a%20bed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fb5aef4af076d3cf923dd2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C