20and%20position%20your%20back%20against%20the%20straight%20side.%20It's%20a%20popular%20choice%20for%20side%20sleepers%20to%20curl%20up%20with.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFill%20and%20Firmness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDetermine%20your%20preferred%20firmness%20level%2C%20balancing%20proper%20spinal%20alignment%20with%20comfort.%20Factors%20such%20as%20weight%2C%20height%2C%20and%20sleeping%20position%20influence%20this%20choice.%20Most%20of%20the%20body%20pillows%20we've%20examined%20have%20a%20memory%20foam%20or%20down-alternative%20fill%2C%20but%20body%20pillows%20are%20available%20in%20all%20the%20typical%20fillings%20of%20pillows%20including%20down%2C%20wool%2C%20and%20latex%20as%20well.%20Memory%20foam%20pillows%20are%20firmer%20and%20offer%20more%20support%2C%20while%20down-alternative%20and%20polyfill%20will%20sleep%20more%20plush.%C2%A0%20Opt%20for%20hypoallergenic%20options%2C%20and%20for%20foam%20fill%2C%20ensure%20it's%20CertiPUR-US%20certified.%20Always%20check%20if%20the%20materials%20are%20safe%20and%20certified%20for%20a%20worry-free%20sleeping%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EEase%20of%20cleaning%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EConsider%20the%20ease%20of%20cleaning%2C%20with%20some%20body%20pillows%20featuring%20removable%2C%20washable%20covers%20(e.g.%2C%20Coop%20Home%20and%20Tempur-Pedic).%20Even%20those%20without%20removable%20covers%2C%20like%20the%20Snuggle-Pedic%20and%20Zoma%2C%20can%20be%20machine-washed.%20A%20pillowcase%20is%20recommended%20for%20regular%20washing%2C%20though%20washing%20larger%20pillows%20may%20be%20time-consuming.%20As%20body%20pillows%20increase%20in%20popularity%2C%20more%20bedding%20brands%20offer%20body%20pillow%20covers%3B%20just%20be%20sure%20to%20match%20the%20dimensions%20of%20your%20pillow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETemperature%20regulation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20sleep%20hot%2C%20opt%20for%20a%20breathable%20pillow%20designed%20to%20regulate%20temperature.%20Some%2C%20like%20the%20Snuggle-Pedic%2C%20use%20materials%20to%20dissipate%20body%20heat%20effectively.%20Breathability%20is%20crucial%2C%20as%20overheating%20can%20disrupt%20sleep%20quality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMedina%20emphasizes%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20want%20to%20become%20overheated%20on%20the%20body%20pillow%2C%20as%20an%20increased%20body%20temperature%20can%20provoke%20a%20wake%20response.%26quot%3B%20A%20good%20body%20pillow%20enhances%20support%2C%20comfort%2C%20and%20breathability%20for%20improved%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EReturn%20policy%2FTrial%20Period%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPrioritize%20pillows%20with%20a%20flexible%20return%20policy%20and%20trial%20period.%20Since%20side%20sleepers%20may%20need%20time%20to%20find%20the%20perfect%20fit%2C%20allowing%20at%20least%20a%20week%20to%20adjust%20is%20essential.%20Ensure%20you%20can%20exchange%20or%20return%20the%20pillow%20if%20it%20doesn't%20meet%20your%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20body%20pillows%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20body%20pillows%20stacked%20on%20top%20of%20each%20other%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20paisley%20print%20sheet.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608c274a34af8d001859a33a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBody%20pillows%20typically%20some%20in%20either%20an%20I-%2C%20C-%2C%20or%20U-shape.%20The%20ones%20shown%20here%20are%20all%20I-shape%20pillows.%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Hernandez%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20managed%20a%20sleep%20laboratory%20for%20over%20two%20years%20and%20have%20conducted%20a%20vast%20amount%20of%20research%20on%20sleep.%20I've%20tested%20products%20for%20SleepScore%20labs%20and%20presented%20my%20work%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.easternpsychological.org%2Fi4a%2Fpages%2Findex.cfm%3Fpageid%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEastern%20Psychological%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20the%20best%20body%20pillows%2C%20I%20did%20hands-on%20testing%20with%20nine%20different%20models%3B%20relied%20on%20my%20background%20in%20sleep%20research%3B%20and%20interviewed%20sleep%20expert%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flivelovesleep.com%2Fzeke-medina-adult-sleep-consultant-and-health-consultant%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZeke%20Medina%2C%20PharmD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20physical%20therapist%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkarenlitzy.com%2Fdr-karen-litzy-pt-dpt%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKaren%20Litzy%2C%20DPT%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20sleep%20researcher%20and%20certified%20sleep%20science%20consultant%2C%20it's%20important%20for%20me%20to%20review%20items%20that%20truly%20improve%20quality%20sleep.%20I%20paid%20close%20attention%20to%20how%20well%20I%20slept%20with%20each%20pillow%2C%20including%20how%20comfortable%2C%20breathable%2C%20and%20supportive%20they%20were.%20Here's%20how%20I%20evaluated%20each%20pillow%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESetup%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20First%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20know%20whether%20the%20body%20pillows%20emitted%20any%20chemical%20odors%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20opened%20the%20package.%20If%20there%20was%20an%20odor%2C%20I%20evaluated%20how%20long%20it%20took%20for%20any%20smells%20to%20dissipate.%20I%20also%20noted%20if%20the%20pillows%20were%20adjustable%20and%20if%20they%20included%20a%20removable%20and%20washable%20cover.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecs%20and%20components%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20recorded%20each%20body%20pillow's%20length%2C%20weight%2C%20firmness%2C%20and%20quality%20of%20materials.%20I%20also%20noted%20if%20they%20were%20hypoallergenic%20and%20researched%20if%20the%20pillows'%20fills%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcertipur.us%2Fabout-the-seal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECertiPUR-US%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecertified%20or%20made%20without%20toxic%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESleeping%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20slept%20with%20each%20body%20pillow%20for%20seven%20consecutive%20nights%2C%20taking%20note%20of%20how%20well%20I%20was%20able%20to%20fall%20asleep%2C%20how%20well%20I%20stayed%20asleep%2C%20and%20how%20I%20felt%20in%20the%20morning.%20I%20evaluated%20how%20comfortable%20and%20soft%20the%20materials%20were%2C%20whether%20I%20slept%20cool%20or%20hot%2C%20and%20how%20much%20support%20and%20tension%20relief%20I%20felt%20throughout%20the%20night%20and%20in%20the%20morning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReturn%20policy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20return%20policy%20and%20warranty%20of%20each%20pillow.%20This%20is%20important%2C%20in%20case%20individuals%20are%20unsure%20it's%20the%20right%20fit.%20%26quot%3BNo%20single%20pillow%20is%20the%20answer%20for%20everybody%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Medina%2C%20so%20it's%20best%20to%20try%20out%20body%20pillows%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20works%20for%20you.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong-term%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESince%20original%20testing%2C%20I've%20continued%20to%20use%20our%20top%20picks%20regularly%20and%20will%20report%20back%20about%20their%20durability%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EBody%20pillow%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Six%20body%20pillows%20lined%20up%20next%20to%20each%20other.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608c269b34af8d001859a332%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20body%20pillow%20can%20help%20alleviate%20strain%20caused%20by%20injury%2C%20pregnancy%2C%20or%20a%20bad%20mattress.%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Hernandez%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20are%20body%20pillows%20used%20for%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20benefits%20you%20get%20from%20a%20body%20pillow%2