our%20needs.%20However%2C%20there's%20a%20new%20contender%20worth%20considering%20for%20this%20category%3A%20the%20Pluto%20Puff%20body%20pillow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20weighing%2012%20pounds%2C%20the%20Puff%20is%20surprisingly%20easy%20to%20maneuver.%20The%20medium-firm%20feel%20supports%20side%20sleepers%20to%20keep%20their%20head%2C%20neck%2C%20and%20spine%20aligned%20through%20the%20night.%20Pluto%20Puff%20is%20built%20with%20side%20sleepers%20in%20mind%2C%20it's%20flexible%2C%20soft%2C%20and%20durable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20side%20sleeper%2C%20I%20know%20how%20tough%20it%20can%20be%20to%20find%20a%20comfortable%20position%20with%20all%20that%20pressure%20on%20the%20shoulders%2C%20hips%2C%20and%20knees.%20The%20Puff%20provides%20ample%20support%20in%20all%20the%20right%20areas%2C%20making%20it%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20relieving%20pressure%20points%20and%20reducing%20tossing%20and%20turning.%20My%20husband%2C%20with%20sleep%20apnea%2C%20finds%20relief%20by%20sleeping%20on%20his%20side%20instead%20of%20his%20back.%20He%20reported%20the%20Puff%20to%20be%20incredibly%20helpful%20in%20maintaining%20proper%20alignment%20on%20his%20head%20and%20neck%2C%20with%20just%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20elevation.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pluto%20Puff%20stood%20out%20as%20one%20of%20the%20best%20body%20pillows%20I've%20tested.%20Not%20only%20does%20it%20boast%20high-quality%20materials%2C%20but%20the%20included%20pillow%20case%20feels%20incredibly%20luxurious%2C%20silky%20smooth%2C%20and%20so%20soft%2C%20like%20cuddling%20up%20with%20a%20cozy%20cloud%20of%20comfort.%20The%20Pluto%20Puff%20is%20an%20excellent%20option%2C%20especially%20for%20side%20sleepers.%20It%20held%20its%20shape%20over%20time%20while%20providing%20consistent%20comfort%2C%20proper%20spinal%20alignment%2C%20and%20reliable%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20back%20pain%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Tempur%20Pedic%20body%20pill