Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20cooling%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Zoma%20pillow%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20paisley%20print%20sheet%2C%20in%20its%20original%20packaging.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608c1c1534af8d001859a27d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZoma%20makes%20an%20exceptional%20cooling%20body%20pillow%20that%20is%20great%20for%20hot%20sleepers.%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Hernandez%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Zoma%20Sleep%20Body%20Pillow%20is%20made%20with%20high-quality%20materials%20that%20kept%20me%20cool%20and%20comfortable%20throughout%20the%20night.%20The%20cover%20is%20made%20from%20a%20blend%20of%20stretchy%2C%20lightweight%20polyester%20and%20spandex.%20It's%20filled%20with%20shredded%20gel%20memory%20foam%20intended%20to%20keep%20hot%20sleepers%20at%20a%20comfortable%20temperature.%20It's%20a%20very%20well-made%2C%20high-quality%20body%20pillow%20that%20provides%20great%20support%20and%20breathability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20somewhat%20firmer%20than%20the%20Coop%20pillow%20but%20still%20provides%20great%20support%20and%20comfort.%20The%206-inch%20loft%20is%20helpful%20for%20side%20sleepers%20like%20me%20who%20need%20support%20between%20the%20knees.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20nights%20sleeping%20with%20the%20Zoma%2C%20I%20noticed%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20my%20posture%20and%20spinal%20alignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Zoma%20Sleep%20is%202%20inches%20shorter%20than%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20possible%20to%20rest%20my%20head%20on%20it%20and%20have%20full%20leg%20support%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20I'm%20relatively%20short%2C%20so%20this%20could%20be%20a%20more%20noticeable%20issue%20for%20taller%20folks%20who%20want%20a%20pillow%20that%20supports%20the%20whole%20body.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20smaller%20size%20could%20be%20perfect%20for%20those%20who%20sleep%20with%20a%2