nations%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehoneymoon%20across%20Asia%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20himself%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20according%20to%20documents%20viewed%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20he%20started%20a%20second%20job%2C%20John%20said%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20had%20plans%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20continent%20in%20some%20capacity%2C%20but%20the%20pandemic%20forced%20them%20to%20postpone%20their%20trip.%20By%20the%20time%20they%20started%20planning%20it%20again%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20later%2C%20their%20financial%20circumstances%20had%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20came%20down%20to%20rescheduling%2C%20I%20was%20overemployed%20already%20%E2%80%94%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20splurge%20a%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20is%20among%20a%20niche%20group%20of%20job%20jugglers%20secretly%20working%20multiple%20jobs.%20Many%20are%20boasting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployed-remote-jobs-workers-millennials-tech-overemployment-retirement-savings-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esix-figure%20incomes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20holding%20on%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-job-openings-decline-as-more-companies-return-to-office-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efully%20remote%20roles%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20have%20become%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomicgraph.linkedin.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fme%2Feconomicgraph%2Fen-us%2FPDF%2Fglobal-state-of-remote-and-hybrid-work.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextremely%20competitive%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years.%20These%20people%20have%20used%20their%20extra%20earnings%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremployed-jobs-remote-hybrid-work-united-kingdom-overemployment-debt-tech-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epay%20off%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20plan%20for%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foveremploye