%2Findia%2Findia-screwed-up-how-us-lobbied-new-delhi-reverse-laptop-rules-2024-03-21%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20(March%2021).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-a-u-turn-union-govt-rolls-back-plans-to-license-laptop-computer-imports%5C%22%3Ehad%20imposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20import%20curbs%20on%20laptops%2C%20tablets%2C%20and%20certain%20types%20of%20computers%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20reasons%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20need%20to%20promote%20domestic%20manufacturing.%20However%2C%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovt-may-remove-the-requirement-for-mandatory-licence-to-import-laptops-pcs-tablets-report%5C%22%3Erolled%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20move%20that%20had%20rattled%20several%20companies%2C%20including%20US-based%20Apple%2C%20Dell%2C%20and%20HP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20State%20Department%20had%20called%20the%20move%20as%20%E2%80%9Chighly%20protectionist%20and%20out%20of%20sync%20with%20the%20progress%20India%20has%20made%20in%20improving%20the%20investment%20environment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202023%2C%20the%20US%2C%20China%20and%20Korea%20had%20raised%20concerns%20over%20India%E2%80%99s%20move%20in%20a%20WTO%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2026%2C%202023%2C%20days%20after%20the%20import%20restriction%20policy%20was%20announced%2C%20US%20Trade%20Representative%20Katherine%20Tai%20met%20commerce%20minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20USTR%20briefing%20paper%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters%2C%20said%20that%20although%20Tai%20%E2%80%9Craised%20concerns%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20policy%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnoted%E2%80%9D%20that%20stakeholders%20needed%20to%20be%20consulted%2C%20she%20privately%20told%20Goyal%20during%20the%20meeting%20that%20the%20US%20wanted%20India%20to%20%E2%80%9Crescin