2%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%2021st%20Century%20Pushpak%20'Viman'%20Set%20For%20Launch%2C%20D-Day%20Tomorrow%2C%207%20AM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20sleek%2C%20SUV-sized%20winged%20rocket%20is%20ready%20for%20its%20experimental%20flight%20at%20a%20defence%20airfield%20in%20Karnataka.%20The%20rocket%20will%20be%20launched%20at%207%20am%20tomorrow%20from%20the%20Chalakere%20Runway.%20Named%20%26quot%3BPushpak%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Re-usable%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(RLV)%20sometimes%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3Bswadeshi%20space%20shuttle%26quot%3B%20is%20India's%20bold%20attempt%20to%20enter%20the%20reusable%20rocket%20segment.%20The%20current%20experiment%20is%20the%20third%20flight%20of%20Pushpak%20--%20all%20part%20of%20a%20test%20of%20its%20robotic%20landing%20ability%20in%20more%20complicated%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Pushpak%20launch%20vehicle%20is%20India's%20bold%20attempt%20to%20make%20access%20to%20space%20most%20affordable%2C%26quot%3B%20asserted%20S%20Somanath%2C%20Chairman%2C%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO).%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20India's%20futuristic%20Reusable%20Launch%20Vehicle%2C%20where%20the%20most%20expensive%20part%2C%20the%20upper%20stage%2C%20which%20houses%20all%20the%20expensive%20electronics%2C%20is%20made%20reusable%20by%20bringing%20it%20back%20safely%20back%20to%20Earth.%20Later%2C%20it%20could%20even%20do%20refuelling%20of%20in-orbit%20satellites%20or%20retrieving%20satellites%20from%20orbit%20for%20refurbishment.%20India%20seeks%20to%20minimise%20space%20debris%20and%20Pushpak%20is%20one%20step%20towards%20that%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20making%20for%20a%20decade%2C%20the%20RLV%20flew%20from%20Sriharikota%20first%20in%202016%20and%20successfully%20landed%20on%20a%20virtual%20runway%20in%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%20The%20RLV%20was%20never%20recovered.%20As%20planned%2C%20it%20sank%20into%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20test%20was%20successfully%20conducted%20on%20April%202%2C%202023%2C%20at%20the%20Chitradurga%20Aeronautical%20Test%20Range%20of%20the%20defence%20establishment.%20Called%20the%20RLV-LEX%2C%20the%20winged%20rocket%20was%20hoisted%20into%20the%20air%20by%20an%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20Chinook%20Helicopter%2C%20slung%20on%20its%20under-carriage%20and%20then%20dropped%20to%20land%20in%20an%20autonomous%20landing%2C%20which%20went%20off%20without%20a%20hitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20name%2C%20Mr%20Somanath%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BPushpak%20Viman%26quot%3B%20is%20India's%20legendary%20spaceship%20named%20in%20the%20Ramayan%2C%20known%20to%20be%20the%20vehicle%20of%20the%20Lord%20of%20Wealth%2C%20God%20Kuber.%20So%20it%20is%20appropriate%20to%20name%20India's%20most%20audacious%2021st%20Century%20rocket%20as%20Pushpak.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20expected%20that%20in%20times%20to%20come%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20money%20spinner%20for%20India%20when%20it%20becomes%20a%20commercially%20available%20launcher.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPushpak%20is%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Sunil%20P%2C%20Program%20Director%2C%20Advanced%20Technology%20%26amp%3B%20Systems%20Group%2C%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Center.%20%26quot%3BISRO%20has%20an%20objective%20to%20fly%20a%20vehicle%20that%20is%20more%20cost-effective%20and%20provides%20very%20low-cost%20access%20to%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20thought%20of%20building%20its%20own%20version%20of%20the%20space%20shuttle%20over%2015%20years%20ago.%20Ten%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20dedicated%20team%20of%20engineers%20and%20scientists%20plunged%20into%20making%20RLV%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%206.5-meter%20aeroplane-like%20space%20craft%20weighs%201.75%20tons%20and%20will%20be%20hoisted%20aboard%20an%20IAF%20helicopter.%20During%20the%20descent%2C%20a%20phase%20which%20is%20essentially%20a%20glider-like%20event%2C%20small%20thrusters%20will%20help%20the%20vehicle%20navigate%20to%20the%20exact%20spot%20where%20it%20is%20supposed%20to%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20invested%20over%20Rs%20100%20crore%20in%20the%20project%2C%20which%20is%20a%20milestone%20as%20the%20country%20moves%20towards%20making%20its%20own%20space%20station%20--%20the%20Bhartiya%20Antariksha%20Station%20--%20by%202035.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711021440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fjvviemdk_pushpak-_625x300_21_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-21st-century-pushpak-viman-ready-to-take-flight-5283011%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20sleek%2C%20SUV-sized%20winged%20rocket%20is%20ready%20for%20its%20experimental%20flight%20at%20a%20defence%20airfield%20in%20Karnataka.%20The%20rocket%20will%20be%20launched%20at%207%20am%20tomorrow%20from%20the%20Chalakere%20Runway.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-21st-century-pushpak-viman-ready-to-take-flight-5283011%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-21st-century-pushpak-viman-ready-to-take-flight-5283011%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-21st-century-pushpak-viman-ready-to-take-flight-5283011%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre's%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20On%20Hold%3A%20The%20Case%20By%20Kunal%20Kamra%2C%20Editors%20Guild%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20pause%20on%20the%20Centre's%20move%20to%20notify%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20under%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20followed%20arguments%20by%20the%20counsel%20of%20stand-up%20comic%20Kunal%20Kamra%20and%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%2C%20flagging%20concerns%20over%20freedom%20of%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20today%20set%20aside%20the%20ruling%20by%20a%20single-judge%20bench%20of%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20that%20had%20said%20no%20grave%20loss%20would%20be%20caused%20if%20the%20Centre%20sets%20up%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20have%20expressed%20concerns%20of%20censorship%20and%20said%20the%20new%20IT%20rules%2C%20under%20which%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20was%20notified%2C%20would%20restrict%20users%20from%20expressing%20themselves%20freely%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Petitioners%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChallenging%20the%20ruling%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Darius%20Khambata%2C%20appearing%20for%20Mr%20Kamra%2C%20said%20the%20new%20IT%20rules%20will%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bchilling%20effect%20on%20free%20speech%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20rules%20introduced%20last%20year%2C%20if%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20comes%20across%20any%20post%20that%20is%20fake%2C%20false%2C%20and%20contains%20misleading%20facts%20about%20the%20business%20of%20the%20government%2C%20it%20would%20flag%20them%20to%20social%20media%20intermediaries.%20Once%20such%20a%20post%20is%20flagged%2C%20the%20intermediary%20has%20the%20option%20of%20taking%20it%20down%20or%20putting%20a%20disclaimer.%20In%20taking%20the%20second%20option%2C%20the%20intermediary%20risks%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khambata%20today%20said%20social%20media%20intermediaries%20might%20take%20down%20content%20flagged%20by%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20instead%20of%20taking%20any%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%20they%20will%2C%20why%20will%20they%20take%20that%20risk.%20It%20has%20a%20chilling%20effect%20on%20free%20speech.%20No%20intermediary%20challenged%20these%20rules.%20Why%3F%20Because%20they%20will%20protect%20their%20interests.%20They%20will%20happily%20be%20chilled%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Bar%20%26amp%3B%20Bench%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khambata%20said%20the%20new%20rules%20focused%20on%20protecting%20the%20Centre.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20question%20of%20Caesar%20judging%20Caesar.%20Centre%20is%20not%20a%20separate%20class.%20If%20the%20object%20is%20to%20prevent%20fake%20news%2C%20everyone%20is%20affected.%20Individuals%20even%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElections%20are%20coming%2C%20public%20must%20have%20all%20information%20about%20the%20government.%20Not%20information%20filtered%20out%20as%20fake%20by%20Centre%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20lawyer%20also%20said%20the%20government's%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20was%20the%20biggest%20irony%20because%20a%20government%20arm%20is%20supposed%20to%20put%20out%20correct%20information%20about%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20the%20Editors%20Guild%2C%20Advocate%20Shadan%20Farasat%20said%20the%20government%20dictating%20whether%20or%20not%20something%20was%20true%20struck%20at%20the%20core%20of%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20-%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20-%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20judges%20(of%20high%20court)%20have%20proceeded%20on%20the%20assumption%20that%20the%20government%20is%20a%20good%20boy.%20The%20critique%20business%20of%20the%20government%20is%20why%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20exists%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Farasat%20said%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20had%20come%20into%20force%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20announcing%20the%20dates%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20stressed%20that%20it%20was%20the%20worst%20time%20to%20notify%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20will%20investigative%20journalist%20work%20at%20all%3F%20It%20is%20through%20several%20sources%20in%20the%20government.%20Now%20a%20central%20authority%20will%20stamp%20out%20all%20other%20voices.%20It%20even%20impacts%20the%20disputed%20question%20between%20Centre%20and%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20had%20delivered%20a%20split%20verdict%20and%20the%20case%20moved%20to%20a%20single-judge%20bench%2C%20which%20refused%20relief%20to%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Centre%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20rules%20were%20issued%20in%20the%20public%20interest%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20fake%20news.%20Political%20opinions%2C%20satire%20and%20comedy%20are%20not%20linked%20to%20government%20business%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20argued%2C%20but%20petitioners%20say%20'business%20of%20the%20Central%20Government'%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bvague%26quot%3B%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20today%20said%20the%20online%20medium%20was%20uncontrollable%20and%20spanned%20across%20borders.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20bothered%20government%20is%20that%20false%20news%20of%20the%20government%20being%20flashed%20across%20intermediaries.%20Like%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20huge%20covid%20influx%20and%20then%20people%20start%20queuing%20up%20for%20grains%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mehta%20clarified%20that%20it%20would%20be%20restricted%20to%20government%20business.%20%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20criticises%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20it%20would%20not%20fall%20under%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Supreme%20Court%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20Justice%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20noted%20that%20the%20final%20hearing%20on%20the%20challenge%20to%20the%20new%20IT%20rules%20would%20begin%20in%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20on%20April%2015.%20It%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20single-judge%20bench's%20order%20came%20did%20not%20pause%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20because%20it%20had%20not%20been%20notified%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20noted%20that%20the%20challenge%20to%20the%20validity%20of%20IT%20Rules%20involves%20serious%20constitutional%20questions%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20free%20speech%20and%20expression%20would%20need%20to%20be%20analysed%20by%20the%20high%20court.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20paused%20the%20notification%2C%20but%20noted%20that%20it%20is%20not%20commenting%20on%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711021200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-01%2Fguk7mua_kunal-kamra_625x300_29_January_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-fact-check-unit-on-hold-the-case-by-kunal-kamra-editors-guild-5283034%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court's%20pause%20on%20the%20Centre's%20move%20to%20notify%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20under%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20followed%20arguments%20by%20the%20counsel%20of%20stand-up%20comic%20Kunal%20Kamra%20and%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-fact-check-unit-on-hold-the-case-by-kunal-kamra-editors-guild-5283034%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-fact-check-unit-on-hold-the-case-by-kunal-kamra-editors-guild-5283034%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-fact-check-unit-on-hold-the-case-by-kunal-kamra-editors-guild-5283034%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Imtiaz%20Ali%20picks%20between%20Deepika%20and%20Kareena%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711020970000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108680269%2Cimgsize-273576.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwho-is-the-better-performer-between-kareena-kapoor-and-deepika-padukone-imtiaz-ali-takes-h