0parties%2C%20anonymously%20takes%20the%20problems%20of%20independence%20to%20another%20level.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20explores%20some%20of%20the%20linkages%20between%20media%2C%20big%20business%20and%20political%20funding%20the%20SBI%20and%20EC%20data%20has%20revealed.%20Electoral%20bonds%20could%20be%20pointers%20to%20how%20the%20information%20ecosystem%20of%20our%20country%20is%20greatly%20influenced%20by%20whom%20it%20is%20meant%20to%20interrogate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EQwik%20Supply%20Chain%20Private%20Limited%3A%20Rs%20410%20Crore%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ftop-electoral-bond-purchasers-include-some-companies-that-were-raided-or-under-the-scanner%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20reported%20by%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20March%2015%2C%20Qwik%20Supply%20Chain%20Private%20Limited%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20company%20which%20bought%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%20410%20crore%2C%20has%20strong%20links%20with%20Mukesh%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20Reliance%20group.%20According%20to%20the%20company%20information%20available%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaubacorp.com%2Fcompany%2FQWIK-SUPPLY-CHAIN-PRIVATE-LIMITED%2FU51100MH2000PTC129528%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Zauba%20Corp%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20two%20present%20directors%20are%20Vipul%20Pranlal%20Mehta%20and%20Tapas%20Mitra.%20According%20to%20Zauba%20Corp%2C%20Tapas%20Mitra%2C%20is%20also%20the%20director%20of%20Reliance%20Oil%20and%20Petroleum%2C%20Reliance%20Eros%20Productions%2C%20Reliance%20Photo%20Films%2C%20Reliance%20Fire%20Brigades%2C%20Ral%20Investment%20Private%20Limited%2C%20Reliance%20First%20Private%20Limited%2C%20Reliance%20Polyester%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20data%20on%20the%20EC%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20Qwik%20Supply%20Chain%20made%20its%20first%20purchase%20of%20bonds%20on%20January%205%2C%202022.%20The%20second%20batch%20of%20purchases%20took%20place%20five%20days%20later%2C%20on%20January%2010.%20This%20was%20followed%20on%20November%2011%2C%202022%20and%20a%20year%20later%20on%20November%2017%2C%202023.%20All%20electoral%20bond%20purchases%20were%20made%20in%20bonds%20of%20denomination%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20each.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0The%20Reliance%20media%20footprint%20with%20CNBC-TV18%20on%20television%20screens%20has%20fast%20morphed%20onto%20multiple%20levels%20of%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ril.com%2Fbusinesses%2Fmedia-entertainment%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20Reliance%20Industries%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20media%20houses%2C%20with%20an%20omni-channel%20presence%2C%20bringing%20authentic%20news%20and%20wholesome%20entertainment%20to%20diverse%20Indian%20audiences.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Network18%20Media%20%26amp%3B%20Investments%20(Network18)%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Conly%20Media%20%26amp%3B%20Entertainment%20conglomerate%20with%20presence%20across%20the%20full%20spectrum%20of%20content%20genres%20%E2%80%93%20news%2C%20entertainment%2C%20sports%2C%20movies%2C%20and%20live%20entertainment.%E2%80%9D%20They%20speak%20of%20being%20committed%20to%20more%20investments%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENews18.com%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMoneycontrol.com%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20Voot%20(an%20over-the-top%20or%20OTT%20media%20service).%20Jio%20Cinemas%20with%20the%20popular%20cricket%20streaming%20has%20further%20strengthened%20its%20dominance%20over%20the%20infotainment%20universe.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Of%20late%2C%20this%20group%20is%20said%20to%20be%20preparing%20for%20an%20even%20larger%20media%20footprint.%20On%20February%2028%2C%20Reliance%20Industries%2C%20Viacom18%20Media%20and%20The%20Walt%20Disney%20Corporation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-disney-form-joint-venture-to-merge-tv-ott-business-in-india-124022801085_1.html%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ehave%20entered%20an%20agreement%20to%20form%20a%20joint%20venture%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20would%20merge%20the%20television%20and%20digital%20streaming%20businesses%20of%20Viacom18%20and%20Star%20India%20and%20create%20an%20entertainment%20giant%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%20A%20joint%20statement%20put%20the%20valuation%20at%20approximately%20%248.5%20billion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20have%20been%20concerns%20about%20this%20becoming%20a%20monopoly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fdisney-reliance-merger-deal-indian-media-1235925129%2F%5C%22%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVariety%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20magazine%20wrote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20combination%20of%20the%20two%20%E2%80%93%20which%20include%20rival%20streaming%20platforms%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20leading%20pay-TV%20platform%20and%20over%20100%20linear%20TV%20channels%20%E2%80%93%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20substantially%20re-shape%20the%20Indian%20media%20and%20entertainment%20scene%20and%20command%20a%2040%25%20market%20share.%E2%80%9D%20The%20new%20venture%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20have%20over%20750%20million%20viewers%20across%20India%20and%20will%20also%20cater%20to%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20across%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20companies%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Laxmidas%20Vallabhdas%20Asmita%20Mercha%E2%80%99%3A%20Rs%2025%20Crore%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndividuals%20have%20also%20bought%20electoral%20bonds.%20Of%20the%20total%20of%20374%20individuals%20who%20have%20bought%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%20384%20crore%2C%20as%20per%20BusinessLine%2C%20Lakshmi%20Mittal%20topped%20the%20list%2C%20but%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fdata-stories%2Fdata-focus%2Fnot-just-companies-individuals-have-also-bought-bonds%2Farticle67954888.ece%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eat%20number%20two%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20Laxmidas%20Vallabhdas%20Asmita%20Mercha%2C%20as%20per%20the%20SBI%20list%2C%20one%20of%20two%20persons%20who%20has%20bought%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2025%20crore%20each.%20Assumed%20to%20be%20a%20mis-spelling%20for%20Laxmidas%20Vallabhdas%20Merchant%2C%20who%20is%20Group%20Controller%20of%20Reliance%20Industries%20Ltd%20and%20listed%20as%20a%20director%20with%20Reliance%20Life%20Sciences%2C%20and%20many%20more%20Reliance%20companies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reporters-collective.in%2Ftrc%2Freliance-accounts-man-among-the-top-100-electoral-bonds-donors%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Reporters%2527%2520Collective%2520compared%2520publicly%2Creleased%2520by%2520the%2520Election%2520Commission.%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20Reporter%E2%80%99s%20Collective%20has%20identified%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20least%20six%20of%20the%20companies%20he%20is%20director%20in%2C%20which%20enabled%20Reliance%20to%20takeover%20the%20media%20group%2C%20Network%2018.%20Asmita%20Merchant%20is%20%E2%80%9Crelated%20to%E2%80%9D%20Laxmidas%20V.%20Merchant%2C%20as%20per%20public%20information%20available%2C%20analysed%20by%20the%20Collective.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bonds%20bought%20by%20this%20individual%20donor%20were%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20each%3B%20all%2025%20bonds%20purchased%20on%20the%20same%20date%2C%20November%2017%2C%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20another%20instance%20of%20how%20different%20business%20groups%20exercise%20indirect%20hold%20over%20media%20groups%2C%20a%20company%2C%20Media%20Matrix%20Worldwide%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Reliance%20group%20has%20a%20small%20stake%20owns%20MN%20Media%20Ventures%20which%20purchased%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%205%20crore%20in%20November%202022%2C%20and%20also%20NexG%20Devices%20which%20spent%20Rs%2035%20crore%20on%20bonds%20in%20May%202019%20and%20November%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20board%20members%20of%20NexG%20Devices%20is%20Surendra%20Lunia%2C%20former%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20associate%20who%20sold%20his%2029.18%25%20stake%20in%20NDTV%20held%20by%20Reliance%20to%20the%20Adani%20group.%20This%20allowed%20the%20Adani%20group%20to%20do%20a%20hostile%20takeover%20of%20NDTV%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20Lunia%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20board%20member%20in%20Infotel%20Business%20Solutions%2C%20Infotel%20Enterprises%2C%20and%20Mankind%20Pharma%20which%20together%20with%20NexG%20made%20donations%20worth%20Rs%2079%20crore%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESun%20TV%20network%3A%20Rs%2010%20Crore%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20sealed%20cover%20declarations%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20which%20were%20made%20public%20on%20Sunday%2C%20March%2017%2C%20the%20DMK%20has%20declared%20that%20it%20received%20Rs%2010%20crore%20in%20donation%20from%20Sun%20TV%20Network%20Limited.%20This%20was%20received%2C%20it%20said%2C%20between%20April%205%2C%202021%20and%20January%2011%2C%202022.%20This%20was%20part%20of%20a%20haul%20of%20Rs%20306%20crore%20in%20this%20span%20of%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETamil%20Nadu-based%20Sun%20TV%20was%20founded%20by%20Kalanithi%20Maran%20in%201993.%20Two%20radio%20stations%20run%20by%20this%20mega%20media%20house%2C%20bought%20Rs%207%20crore%20worth%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20on%20April%203%2C%202021.%20Kal%20Radio%20Limited%20and%20South%20Asia%20FM%20Limited%20purchased%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%203.5%20crore%20and%20Rs%203.5%20crore%2C%20respectively%20in%20different%20denominations.%20Sun%20distribution%20network%20bought%20three%20bonds%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20each%20on%20the%20same%20day.%20Assembly%20elections%20for%20Assam%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Puducherry%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20West%20Bengal%20were%20being%20held%20at%20the%20time.%20Incidentally%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Puducherry%20voted%20three%20days%20after%20these%20bonds%20were%20bought.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sun.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESun%20TV%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%2035%20TV%20channels%20in%20six%20languages.%20It%20claims%20to%20reach%20140%20million%20Indian%20households%20and%20also%20has%20a%20footprint%20across%2027%20countries.%20It%20has%2069%20FM%20radio%20stations%2C%20three%20daily%20newspapers%20and%20six%20magazines.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20DTH%20(Direct%20To%20Home%20Satellite%20TV)%20service%20providers%20in%20India.%20It%20has%20a%20film%20division%20called%20Sun%20Pictures.%20The%20group%20also%20owns%20the%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad%20team%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20%26amp%3B%20SunRisers%20Eastern%20Cape%20in%20the%20South%20Africa%20T20%20League%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMegha%20Engineering%3A%20Rs%20966%20Crore%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20top%20two%20donors%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20was%20Megha%20Engineering%20and%20Infrastructure%20Ltd%2C%20which%20incidentally%20also%20owns%2C%20albeit%20indirectly%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20television%20news%20networks%20TV9Bharatvarsh.%20The%20Hindi%20news%20channel%20is%20owned%20by%20Associated%20Broadcast%20in%20which%20the%20infrastructure%20giant%20is%20a%20majority%20stakeholder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20channel%20is%20known%20for%20its%20pro-government%20coverage%2C%20and%20has%20mostly%20underplayed%20the%20coverage%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds.%20According%20to%20the%20ECI%20data%2C%20Megha%20Engineering%20spent%20Rs%20966%20crore%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20between%20April%2C%202019%20and%20January%202024.%20The%20figure%20may%20be%20higher%20if%20we%20include%20its%20unpublished%20donations%20in%202018-19.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMedia%20groups%20owned%20by%20corporate%20groups%20often%20function%20as%20either%20a%20prestige%20project%20or%20a%20lobbying%20and%20a%20pressure%20group%20for%20its%20original%20business%20interests.%20By%20now%2C%20it%20is%20public%20knowledge%20that%20Megha%20Engineering%20has%20bagged%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ftop-electoral-bond-purchasers-include-some-companies-that-were-raided-or-under-the-scanner%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emultiple%20central%20and%20state%20infrastructure%20projects%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20running%20into%20thousands%20of%20crores%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20one%20of%20its%20recent%20stories%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fnews%2Fpress-money-and-polls-meet-the-media-owners-who-bought-electoral-bonds-2%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3ENews%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%20described%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20how%20electoral%20bonds%20was%20covered%20in%20TV9%20Bharatvarsh%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETake%20TV9%20Bharatvarsh%2C%20where%20Samajwadi%20Party%20spokesperson%20Sunil%20Sajan%20said%20%E2%80%9Cno%20big%20journalist%E2%80%9D%20was%20speaking%20about%20electoral%20bonds%20or%20whether%20central%20agency%20action%20had%20influenced%20their%20purchase.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAayega%20toh%20Modi%20hi%2C%20par%20kaise%20aayega%20Modi%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%20(%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20be%20Modi%20who%20wins%2C%20but%20how%20will%20he%20win%3F%E2%80%9D).%20In%20response%2C%20anchor%20Gaurav%20Agrawal%20turned%20the%20discussion%20around%20to%20ask%20panellists%20how%20Modi%20might%20win%20the%20upcoming%20polls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESanjiv%20Goenka%20Group%3A%20Rs%20609%20Crore%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20companies%20associated%20with%20industrialist%20Sanjiv%20Goenka%20that%20have%20spent%20hugely%20on%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20too%2C%20have%20a%20large%20media%20footprint.%20The%20Sanjiv%20Goenka%20group%20donated%20Rs%20709%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%20609%20crore%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20Rs%20100%20crore%20through%20electoral%20trusts%20%E2%80%93%20in%20political%20funding%20since%20May%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EECI%20data%20reveals%20that%20the%20Sanjiv%20Goenka%20group%20bought%20electoral%20bonds%20through%20its%20five%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20Haldia%20Energy%20Ltd%2C%20Dhariwal%20Infrastructure%20Ltd%2C%20Philips%20Carbon%20Black%20Ltd%2C%20known%20as%20PCBL%20from%202022%20onwards%2C%20Crescent%20Power%20Ltd%2C%20and%20RPSG%20Ventures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERPSG%20Ventures%20that%20spent%20Rs%203%20crore%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20directly%20owns%20%3Cem%3EOpen%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20English%20weekly%20magazine%2C%20%3Cem%3EEditorji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20digital%20news%20platform%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EFortune%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20last%20few%20years%20have%20seen%20Open%20taking%20a%20decidedly%20pro-BJP%20stand.%20The%20Open%20Media%20Network%20removed%20its%20political%20editor%20Hartosh%20Singh%20Bal%2C%20who%20was%20critical%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20Its%20former%20editor%20Manu%20Joseph%20had%20then%20claimed%20that%20Sanjiv%20Goenka%20had%20told%20him%20that%20Bal%E2%80%99s%20views%20was%20%E2%80%9Cmaking%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20enemies%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20business%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20these%20news%20platforms%2C%20the%20group%20also%20owns%20lifestyle%20magazines%20like%20%3Cem%3EEsquire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20the%20to-be-launched%20%3Cem%3EHollywood%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EReporter%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20another%20curious%20case%20is%20of%20the%20Goa-based%20influential%20business%20group%20Dempo%20Industries.%20The%20company%2C%20along%20with%20its%20subsidiaries%2C%20spent%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20on%20electoral%20bonds.%20The%20company%2C%20which%20has%20interests%20in%20ore%20mining%2C%20shipbuilding%2C%20food%20processing%20and%20other%20things%20owns%20the%20%3Cem%3ENavhind%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20leading%20daily%20in%20Goa%20and%20%3Cem%3ENavprabha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Marathi%20daily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20company%20is%20also%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711020657000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21153158%2FUntitled-design-15.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Felectoral-bonds-big-media-donors%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Owners%20of%20many%20large%20and%20influential%20news%20television%20networks%2C%20radio%20stations%2C%20newspapers%2C%20magazines%2C%20portals%20and%20OTT%20have%20emerged%20as%20political%20donors.%20Questions%20about%20media%20being%20an%20effective%20%E2%80%98fourth%20pillar%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99%20have%20sprung%20up%20as%20its%20ties%20with%20big%20business%20and%20now%20political%20funding%20have%20been%20partially%20unveiled.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Felectoral-bonds-big-media-donors%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Power%2C%20Paranoia%20and%20Politics%20Mark%20Series%20Mania%20Thriller%20%E2%80%98In%20the%20Shadows%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711020600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FM