to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday.%20One%20of%20the%20points%20of%20the%20affidavit%20reads%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20respectfully%20submitted%20that%20SBI%20has%20now%20disclosed%20all%20details%20and%20that%20no%20details%20%5Bother%20than%20complete%20account%20numbers%20%26amp%3B%20KYC%20details%5D%20have%20been%20withheld%20from%20disclosure.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20given%20by%20the%20bank%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20uploaded%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20on%20its%20website%20shortly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SBI%20had%20earlier%20given%20two%20lists%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20which%20were%20released%20by%20the%20poll%20panel%20on%20its%20website%20on%20March%2014.%20The%20first%20had%20the%20names%20of%20the%20donors%2C%20the%20denominations%20of%20the%20bonds%2C%20and%20the%20dates%20on%20which%20they%20were%20purchased.%20The%20other%20had%20names%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20as%20well%20as%20the%20denominations%20of%20the%20bonds%20and%20the%20dates%20on%20which%20they%20were%20encashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20the%20unique%20alphanumeric%20code%2C%20however%2C%20there%20was%20no%20way%20of%20linking%20the%20lists%20and%20finding%20out%20which%20donor%20had%20given%20money%20to%20which%20party.%20The%20alphanumeric%20code%20can%20only%20be%20seen%20using%20ultraviolet%20(UV)%20light.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20the%20SBI%20to%20disclose%20all%20details%20related%20to%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20including%20the%20serial%20numbers%2C%20by%205%20pm%20today%20and%20also%20file%20an%20affidavit%20to%20that%20effect.%20The%20direction%20had%20come%20in%20response%20to%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20%26quot%3Bincomplete%20data%26quot%3B%20provided%20by%20the%20bank%2C%20which%20is%20India's%20largest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20all%20information%20related%20to%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20be%20disclosed%20which%20is%20in%20your%20possession...%20The%20SBI's%20attitude%20seems%20to%20be%20'you%20tell%20us%20what%20to%20disclose%2C%20we%20will%20disclose'.%20That%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20fair.%20When%20we%20say%20%26quot%3Ball%20details%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20includes%20all%20conceivable%20data...%20All%20details%20should%20come%20out.%20We%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20nothing%20has%20been%20suppressed%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20affidavit%20on%20Thursday%2C%20which%20bears%20the%20name%20of%20SBI%20Chairman%20Dinesh%20Kumar%20Khara%2C%20the%20bank%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20bears%20repetition%20that%20the%20SBI%20is%20now%20revealing%20information%20%5Balongwith%20that%20already%20disclosed%5D%20which%20will%20show%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20name%20of%20the%20purchaser%20of%20the%20bond%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20denomination%20and%20specific%20number%20of%20the%20bond%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20name%20of%20the%20party%20that%20has%20encashed%20the%20bond%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELast%20four%20digits%20of%20the%20bank%20account%20number%20of%20political%20parties%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20denomination%20and%20number%20of%20the%20bond%20encashed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20also%20asked%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20upload%20the%20details%20once%20it%20got%20them%20from%20the%20SBI%2C%20and%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20happen%20later%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20had%20been%20termed%20unconstitutional%20and%20arbitrary%20and%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20February%2015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711019700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Foc23r498_sbi-state-bank-of-india-reuters_625x300_10_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstate-bank-of-india-submits-all-details-of