'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-rn-ravi-ponmudi-tamil-nadu-governor%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Man%20Complained%20Of%20Chronic%20Headaches%2C%20Now%20He%20Has%2015%20Months%20To%20Live%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERicky%20Smith%2C%2039%2C%20received%20a%20devastating%20diagnosis%20of%20terminal%20cancer.%20This%20news%20comes%20after%20just%20a%20few%20months%20of%20experiencing%20headaches%20he%20initially%20attributed%20to%20work%20stress%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F03%2F20%2Flifestyle%2Fmy-partner-thought-his-bad-headaches-were-from-stress-doctors-now-say-he-has-only-months-to-live%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Smith's%20battle%20began%20in%20February%20with%20persistent%20headaches.%20Believing%20it%20was%20simply%20a%20consequence%20of%20a%20demanding%20workload%2C%20he%20didn't%20seek%20medical%20attention.%20However%2C%20after%20two%20weeks%20with%20no%20improvement%2C%20his%20partner%2C%20Katrina%20Binfield%2C%2041%2C%20urged%20him%20to%20see%20a%20doctor.%20%C2%A0Ms%20Binfield%20claims%20the%20initial%20doctor's%20visit%20yielded%20no%20significant%20diagnosis%2C%20with%20advice%20to%20simply%20rest%20and%20increase%20water%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20pain%20persisted%2C%20prompting%20Ms%20Binfield%20to%20schedule%20Mr%20Smith%20for%20an%20eye%20test.%20This%20appointment%20proved%20crucial%2C%20as%20the%20eye%20doctor%20discovered%20a%20concerning%20sign%20-%20blood%20behind%20both%20of%20Mr%20Smith's%20eyes.%20This%20discovery%20led%20to%20further%20investigation%20and%20ultimately%2C%20the%20life-altering%20diagnosis%20of%20terminal%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20eye%20exam%2C%20Ricky%20was%20urgently%20referred%20to%20Maidstone%20Hospital.**%20There%2C%20a%20CT%20scan%20revealed%20a%20shocking%20discovery%20-%20a%20mass%20on%20his%20brain.%20To%20gain%20a%20clearer%20picture%2C%20doctors%20performed%20an%20MRI%20scan%2C%20which%20confirmed%20the%20worst%3A%20an%20inoperable%20butterfly%20glioblastoma.%20This%20aggressive%20brain%20cancer%20left%20Ricky%20with%20a%20fight%20for%20his%20life%2C%20with%20doctors%20estimating%20he%20has%2015%20months%20to%20live.%20%C2%A0Anxiously%20awaiting%20biopsy%20results%2C%20Mr%20Smith%20hopes%20for%20any%20available%20treatment%20options%20that%20could%20extend%20his%20precious%20time%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Binfield%2C%20a%20make-up%20artist%2C%20from%20Minster%2C%20Isle%20of%20Sheppey%2C%20Kent%2C%20told%20South%20West%20News%20Service%2C%20%26quot%3BLife%20is%20very%20up%20and%20down%20for%20us%20at%20the%20minute.%20There%20are%20days%20when%20Ricky%20can%20be%20confused%20and%20forgetful%20and%20there%20are%20days%20when%20I%20can%20see%20the%20changes%20in%20him.%20That%20is%20really%20hard%2C%20I%20am%20watching%20my%20partner%20change%20in%20front%20of%20my%20eyes.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnMs%20Binfield%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BHe%20started%20getting%20constant%20headaches%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks.%20We%20thought%20at%20first%20it%20may%20have%20been%20a%20virus.%20I%20was%20ill%20just%20before%20but%20his%20lasted%20longer%20than%20mine.%20He%20is%20a%20hardworking%20man%20and%20never%20takes%20time%20off%2C%20but%20he%20was%20starting%20to%20call%20in%20sick%20and%20just%20sit%20around%20the%20house.%20I%20said%20to%20him%20'Rick%20this%20isn't%20you'%20and%20'we%20need%20to%20get%20you%20looked%20at'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Binfield%20said%20that%20sharing%20the%20sad%20news%20with%20their%20children%20-%20Louie%2C%208%2C%20Karson%2C%205%2C%20and%20Arlo%2C%202%20-%20was%20very%20difficult.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArlo%20is%20too%20little%20to%20understand%2C%20but%20I%20sat%20Louie%20and%20Karson%20down%20last%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLouie%20is%20such%20a%20sensitive%20soul%2C%20so%20I%20was%20really%20worried%20about%20him.%20He%20got%20up%2C%20gave%20me%20a%20hug%20and%20said%2C%20'Don't%20worry%2C%20mum%20-%20we%20will%20fight%20this%2C'%20%26quot%3B%20she%20recalled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20she%20and%20Karson%20cried%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20been%20amazing%2C%20but%20it%20still%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20this%20is%20happening%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20revealed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple's%20friends%20set%20up%20a%20GoFundMe%20-%20titled%20%26quot%3BRicks%20army-%20Cancer%20will%20not%20win!!%26quot%3B%20-%20to%20raise%20money%20for%20Smith's%20treatment%2C%20his%2040th%20birthday%20and%20for%20a%20planned%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711017900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Farpdfjm_ricky-smith_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-complained-of-chronic-headaches-now-he-has-15-months-to-live-5282649%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Smith's%20battle%20began%20in%20February%20with%20chronic%20headaches.%20He%20believed%20it%20was%20simply%20work%20stress%2C%20he%20didn't%20seek%20medical%20attention.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-complained-of-chronic-headaches-now-he-has-15-months-to-live-5282649%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-complained-of-chronic-headaches-now-he-has-15-months-to-live-5282649%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-complained-of-chronic-headaches-now-he-has-15-months-to-live-5282649%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rebel%20Wilson%2C%20Charlotte%20Gainsbourg%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98The%20Almond%20And%20T