0in%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsghar%20Ali%20Karbalai%2C%20a%20co-convenor%20of%20KDA%20and%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20lawmaker%2C%20led%20the%20crowd%20as%20it%20rallied%20from%20Fatima%20Chowk%20to%20Hussaini%20Park%20in%20Kargil.%20Karbalai%20urged%20the%20protesters%20to%20brace%20for%20a%20long%20haul%20following%20the%20breakdown%20of%20talks%20with%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Central%20government%20is%20underestimating%20our%20determination.%20They%20believe%20that%20the%20voices%20in%20Ladakh%20can%20be%20quelled%20with%20force.%20But%20we%20must%20stand%20resolute%20and%20prepared%20to%20face%20any%20situation%20in%20the%20fight%20for%20Ladakh%20and%20our%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21142458%2Fc84a33f2-a7a4-4000-a295-46b4826a3355.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21142458%2Fc84a33f2-a7a4-4000-a295-46b4826a3355.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21142458%2Fc84a33f2-a7a4-4000-a295-46b4826a3355-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21142458%2Fc84a33f2-a7a4-4000-a295-46b4826a3355-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702633%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThousands%20of%20people%20gathered%20in%20Kargil%20town%20of%20Ladakh%20to%20extend%20support%20to%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%20who%20has%20been%20on%20a%20fast%20to%20demand%20constitutional%20safeguards%20for%20the%20region.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarbalai%20also%20announced%20that%20along%20with%20Hussain%20and%20Qamar%20Ali%20Akhoon%2C%20a%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20minister%20from%20National%20Conference%20party%20and%20another%20co-convenor%20of%20KDA%2C%20he%20would%20join%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20fast%20which%20entered%20Day%2016%20on%20Thursday%20(March%2021).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWangchuk%2C%20who%20has%20been%20drinking%20only%20water%20and%20salt%20since%20he%20began%20the%20fast%20on%20March%206%2C%20broadcasts%20regular%20video%20messages%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20draw%20the%20attention%20of%20people%20to%20the%20fragile%20environment%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20how%20allowing%20industrial%20setups%20in%20the%20region%20could%20create%20an%20environmental%20catastrophe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20video%20messages%2C%20Wangchuk%20has%20also%20been%20reminding%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20of%20the%20promises%20that%20it%20had%20made%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20in%20its%20poll%20manifestos%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20parliamentary%20election%20and%202020%20Hill%20Council%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20Government%20likes%20to%20call%20India%20the%20%E2%80%98Mother%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99.%20But%20if%20India%20denies%20democratic%20rights%20to%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20%26amp%3B%20continues%20to%20keep%20it%20under%20bureaucrats%20controlled%20from%20New%20Delhi%20then%20it%20could%20only%20be%20called%20a%20Stepmother%20of%20Democracy%20as%20far%20as%20Ladakh%20is%20concerned%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wangchuk%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWangchuk%2C%20who%20has%20been%20leading%20the%20hunger%20strike%20in%20Leh%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20for%20Sixth%20Schedule%20for%20Ladakh%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20also%20planning%20a%20%E2%80%98border%20march%E2%80%99%20of%2010%2C000%20Ladakhi%20shepherds%20and%20farmers%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshow%20the%20ground%20reality%E2%80%9D%20at%20a%20time%20when%20%E2%80%9Cnomads%2