prime%20minister%20to%20cripple%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20financially%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sonia.%20%E2%80%9CFunds%20collected%20from%20the%20public%20are%20being%20frozen%2C%20and%20money%20from%20our%20accounts%20is%20being%20taken%20away%20forcibly.%20However%2C%20even%20under%20these%20most%20challenging%20circumstances%2C%20we%20are%20doing%20our%20best%20to%20maintain%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20our%20election%20campaign.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20last%20month%20declaring%20electoral%20bonds%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20former%20UPA%20chairperson%20said%20that%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20has%20%E2%80%9Cbenefitted%20the%20BJP%20hugely%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20finances%20of%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%2C%20the%20INC%2C%20are%20under%20a%20determined%20assault.%20This%20is%20truly%20unprecedented%20and%20undemocratic%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20party%20had%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-bank-accounts-frozen-election%5C%22%3Efrozen%20its%20bank%20accounts%20%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20demanded%20Rs%20210%20crore%20as%20recovery%20over%20an%20alleged%2045-day%20delay%20in%20filing%20returns%20and%20cash%20contributions%20from%20its%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20upheld%20an%20order%20of%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20(ITAT)%20refusing%20to%20stay%20a%20notice%20issued%20by%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20to%20the%20Congress%20party%20for%20recovery%20of%20outstanding%20tax%20of%20over%20Rs%20100%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IT%20Department%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20Rs%2065.94%20crore%20had%20been%20recovered%20while%20the%20original%20tax%20demand%20stood%20at%20Rs%20102%20crore%20and%20together%20with%20interest%20it%20rose%20to%20Rs%20135.06%20crore%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fdelhi-hc-upholds-itat-order-in-tax-demand-case-involving-congress-party%2Farticleshow%2F108461824.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%20PTI.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20accounts%20frozen%2C%20Rahul%20said%20that%20the%20party%20was%20unable%20to%20purchase%20even%20a%20railway%20ticket%20to%20get%20its%20leaders%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20our%20bank%20accounts%20have%20been%20frozen.%20We%20can%20do%20no%20campaign%20work%2C%20we%20cannot%20support%20our%20candidates.%20They%20cannot%20fly%2C%20forget%20that%2C%20they%20can%20not%20even%20purchase%20a%20rail%20ticket.%20And%20this%20has%20been%20done%20before%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20institutions%20in%20this%20country%20that%20are%20supposed%20to%20protect%20the%20democratic%20framework%20but%20nothing%20is%20happening.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20is%20not%20saying%20anything%2C%20the%20courts%20are%20not%20saying%20anything.%20Our%20ability%20to%20fight%20the%20elections%20have%20been%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20criminal%20action%20done%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20home%20minister.%20The%20idea%20that%20India%20is%20a%20democracy%20is%20a%20lie%2C%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%20is%20a%20lie.%2020%25%20of%20India%20votes%20for%20us%20and%20we%20are%20not%20able%20to%20pay%20Rs%202%20for%20anything.%20This%20is%20being%20orchestrated%20to%20cripple%20us%20in%20the%20elections.%20Even%20if%20our%20accounts%20are%20unfrozen%20today%2C%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20damage%20has%20been%20done.%20And%20no%20one%20is%20saying%20anything-the%20courts%20of%20the%20media%20are%20not%20saying%20anything.%20It%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20as%20you%E2%80%99re%20being%20robbed%20off%20the%20democratic%20structure%20and%20everyone%20is%20quiet%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Maken%2C%20who%20is%20the%20party%20treasurer%2C%20the%20Congress%20received%20a%20notice%20for%20FY%202017-18%2C%20a%20lien%20on%20Rs%20210%20crore%20was%20marked%20in%2011%20accounts%20in%20four%20banks.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20given%20is%20that%20Rs%2014.49%20lakh%20was%20received%20in%20cash%20(as%20donations%20made%20by%20our%20MPs%20to%20the%20Congress%20party)%2C%20out%20of%20total%20receipt%20of%20Rs%20199%20crore.%20This%20cash%20component%20is%20just%200.07%25%20of%20the%20total%20donations.%20And%20the%20punishment%20was%20106%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLook%20at%20the%20timing%20of%20freezing%20our%20accounts.%20We%20received%20the%20Rs%20199%20crore%20donation%20in%202017-18%2C%20but%20after%20seven%20years%2C%20on%20February%2013%2C%202024%2C%20210.25%20crore%20lien%20was%20marked%2C%20our%20bank%20accounts%20were%20virtually%20sealed%2C%20and%20later%2C%20Rs%20115.32%20crore%20was%20forcibly%20confiscated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaken%20said%20that%20the%20party%20received%20another%20notice%20last%20week%20from%20the%20IT%20department%20for%20FY%201993-94%2C%20when%20Sita%20Ram%20Kesari%20was%20the%20treasurer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20being%20asked%20to%20calculate%20penal%20charges%20for%20the%20FY%201993-94%20after%2031%20years%20of%20the%20assessment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20attempting%20to%20deprive%20the%20Congress%20of%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20in%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20leave%20us%20in%20a%20state%20to%20fight%20elections.%20They%20want%20one-sided%20elections.%20Our%20accounts%20should%20be%20unfrozen.%20And%20we%20should%20have%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20said%20that%20it%20will%20move%20court%20and%20explore%20legal%20options%20and%20take%20the%20message%20to%20the%20people%20how%20the%20party%20is%20being%20deprived%20of%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20taking%20the%20message%20to%20the%20people%20through%20press%20conferences.%20This%20is%20my%20third%20press%20conference.%20I%20thought%20the%20senior%20leadership%20should%20be%20present%20to%20take%20the%20message%20to%20the%20people%20and%20we%20have%20done%20that.%20Tomorrow%20PCC%20(Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee)%20presidents%20across%20the%20country%20and%20former%20CMs%20will%20take%20up%20the%20issue%20through%20press%20conferences%20and%20we%20will%20hit%20the%20ground%20and%20spread%20the%20word%20to%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Maken%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711014368000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21151354%2FScreenshot-2024-03-21-at-3.13.15-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdemocracy-frozen-says-congress-calls-action-on-accounts-bid-to-cripple-it-financially%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20party%20said%20that%20it%20had%20received%20two%20notices%20from%20the%20IT%20department%2C%20one%20for%20FY%202017-18%20and%20another%20for%20FY%201993-94%2C%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98systematic%20effort%E2%80%99%20to%20deprive%20the%20Congress%20of%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdemocracy-frozen-says-congress-calls-action-on-accounts-bid-to-cripple-it-financially%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20%E2%80%98Revolving%20Chair%E2%80%99%20of%20Yash%E2%80%99s%20heroine%20in%20Toxic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711014326000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.to