ress%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Patanjali%20said%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20violate%20any%20laws%20while%20advertising%20and%20branding%20its%20products.%20It%20also%20said%20%E2%80%9Cno%20casual%20statements%20claiming%20medicinal%20efficacy%20or%20against%20any%20system%20of%20medicine%20will%20be%20released%20to%20the%20media%20in%20any%20form%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fsupremecourt%2F2022%2F24832%2F24832_2022_11_1_51589_Order_19-Mar-2024.pdf%5C%22%3EBut%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Patanjali%20has%20since%20issued%20advertisements%20violating%20its%20assurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20that%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20Balkrishna%20and%20his%20associate%2C%20the%20yoga%20guru%20Ramdev%2C%20were%20in%20violation%20of%20laws%20prohibiting%20the%20advertisement%20of%20drugs%20relating%20to%20certain%20diseases%20and%20prohibiting%20misleading%20advertisements%20on%20drugs%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fsupreme-court-personal-appearance-baba-ramdev-misleading-patanjali-advertisements%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2027%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%2C%20the%20court%20said%20Patanjali%20continued%20to%20advertise%20medicines%20claiming%20%E2%80%9Cpermanent%20relief%E2%80%9D%20for%20diseases%20and%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftaken-for-a-ride-sc-issues-contempt-notice-to-patanjali-ayurved-its-md-over-misleading-ads%5C%22%3Ethe%20entire%20country%20was%20being%20%E2%80%9Ctaken%20for%20a%20ride%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20slammed%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20its%20lack%20of%20action%20on%20the%20misleading%20advertisements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20sitting%20with%20its%20eyes%20closed.%20This%20is%20very%20unfortunate.%20The%20government%20will%20have%20to%20take%20some%20immediate%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-sitting-with-eyes-closed-must-take-action-says-supreme-court-on-patanjali-misleading-and-false-ads-case-5136445%5C%22%3ENDTV%20quoted%20the%20court%20as%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20banned%20Patanjali%20from%20advertising%20its%20products%20that%20deal%20with%20certain%20diseases%20listed%20under%20the%20Drugs%20and%20Magic%20Remedies%20(Objectionable%20Advertisements)%20Act%2C%201954.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20issued%20show%20cause%20notices%20to%20Patanjali%20and%20to%20Balkrishna%20asking%20why%20it%20should%20not%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fsc-comes-down-heavily-on-patanjali-bars-it-from-advertising-products-meant-for-medical-conditions%2F1980976%2F%5C%22%3Einitiate%20contempt%20of%20court%20proceedings%20against%20them%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20the%20notices%2C%20the%20court%20on%20Tuesday%20(March%2019)%20asked%20Balkrishna%20as%20well%20as%20Ramdev%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20the%20next%20day%20of%20hearing%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20affidavit%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Balkrishna%20reportedly%20also%20said%20the%201954%20Act%20was%20in%20an%20%E2%80%9Carchaic%20state%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRespondent%20No.%205%20Company%20%5BPatanjali%5D%20now%20possess%20evidence-based%20scientific%20data%20with%20clinical%20research%20conducted%20in%20Ayurveda%2C%20which%20would%20demonstrate%20the%20advances%20made%20through%20scientific%20research%20in%20the%20context%20of%20diseases%20mentioned%20in%20the%20said%20schedule%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20affidavit%20also%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fafter-supreme-court-rap-patanjali-md-submits-unqualified-apology-for-publishing-advertisements-o