t%2Fout-of-nearly-1-2-lakh-queries-in-3-years-pibs-fact-check-unit-acted-on-1223%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20PIB%20reveals%20having%20received%20nearly%201.2%20lakh%20requests%20for%20fact%20checking%20information%20on%20the%20internet%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20i.e.%20since%20April%202020%2C%20whereas%20it%20has%20only%20acted%20upon%201%2C223%20of%20them%20%E2%80%93%20a%20modest%201%25%20action%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711010131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F21234509%2FUntitled-design-86-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-stays-union-governments-notification-on-pib-fact-check-unit%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20March%2020%2C%20the%20Union%20electronics%20and%20IT%20ministry%20had%20notified%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau's%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20as%20a%20statutory%20body%20with%20powers%20to%20flag%20what%20it%20believes%20is%20false%20information%20related%20to%20the%20Central%20government%20and%20its%20agencies%20on%20social%20media%20sites.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-stays-union-governments-notification-on-pib-fact-check-unit%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BSEB%20Bihar%20inter%20result%3A%20Here's%20what%20we%20know%20so%20far%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711009957000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108673451%2Cimgsize-120888.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Feducation%2Fnews%2Fbseb-bihar-inter-result-anytime-soon-heres-what-we-know-so-far%2Farticleshow%2F108673287.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20eagerly%20anticipated%20BSEB%20Bihar%20Inter%20or%20Class%2012th%20results%20for%202024%20are%20set%20to%20be%20announced%20soon%2C%20with%20over%2013%20lakh%20students%20awaiting%20their%