%20scam.%20Investigators%20said%20that%20Liao%20lost%20money%20on%20cryptocurrency%20and%20misled%20Zhang%20into%20signing%20a%20legal%20document%20obligating%20Zhang%20to%20pay%20almost%20%24800%2C000.%20He%20also%20told%20Zhang%20that%20some%20gangsters%20were%20after%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%2C%20which%20is%20translated%20from%20Mandarin%2C%20claims%20that%20on%20January%2026%2C%202023%2C%20Zhang%20got%20frostbite%20while%20riding%20a%20motorbike%20with%20his%20friend%20Liao%20in%20Taipei.%20The%20prosecution%20said%20that%20a%20few%20days%20before%20the%20incident%2C%20he%20filed%20for%20life%2C%20health%2C%20and%20accident%20insurance.%20The%20sum%20of%20the%20insurance%20policies%20was%20%241.3%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20the%20two%20returned%20to%20Liao's%20house%2C%20Zhang%20soaked%20his%20feet%20in%20dry%20ice.%20He%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%20after%20the%20foot%20soaking%2C%20where%20medical%20personnel%20thought%20his%20wounds%20were%20fake%2C%20according%20to%20the%20prosecution.%20According%20to%20the%20release%2C%20the%20medical%20staff%20reported%20that%20although%20the%20patient's%20feet%20were%20frostbitten%2C%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bneat%20and%20symmetrical%26quot%3B%20injuries%20and%20%26quot%3Bno%20socks%20or%20shoe%20marks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20reported%20that%20the%20weather%20on%20the%20night%20of%20January%2026%20was%20%26quot%3Bnowhere%20close%20to%20below%20freezing.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAs%20Taiwan%20is%20a%20subtropical%20region%2C%20cases%20of%20severe%20frostbite%20requiring%20amputation%20are%20unheard%20of%20due%20to%20natural%20climatic%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bureau%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZhang%20suffered%20frostbite%20injuries%20which%20necessitated%20the%20amputation%20of%20both%20legs%20below%20the%20calf.%20Nonetheless%2C%20the%20prosecutors%20said%20that%20Zhang's%20case%20was%20reported%20to%20the%20authorities.%20Further%2C%20the%20plastic%20bucket%20that%20was%20used%20to%20freeze%20Zhang's%20feet%2C%20insurance%20papers%2C%20a%20white%20polystyrene%20box%20containing%20dry%20ice%2C%20eight%20cell%20phones%2C%20and%20electronic%20devices%20were%20discovered%20by%20police%20during%20their%20investigation%20of%20Zhang%20and%20Liao%20in%20November.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20bureau%2C%20Liao%20and%20Zhang%20were%20both%20charged%20with%20fraud%20and%20aiding%20and%20abetting%20serious%20injury%20after%20their%20detention%20on%20January%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authorities%20said%20that%20Zhang%20received%20one%20insurance%20payout%20of%20%247%2C200%2C%20however%2C%20it%20will%20be%20seized.%20The%20insurance%20providers%20cancelled%20the%20other%20claims%20filed%20following%20the%20incident%20due%20to%20the%20short%20period%20between%20receiving%20the%20policies%20and%20filing%20them%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711009860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F2nadkba_taiwan-criminal-bureau-_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaiwan-man-persuades-friend-to-get-legs-amputated-for-1-3-million-insurance-scam-5281812%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zhang%20suffered%20frostbite%20injuries%20which%20necessitated%20the%20amputation%20of%20both%20legs%20below%20the%20calf.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaiwan-man-persuades-friend-to-get-legs-amputated-for-1-3-million-insurance-scam-5281812%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaiwan-man-persuades-friend-to-get-legs-amputated-for-1-3-million-insurance-scam-5281812%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaiwan-man-persuades-friend-to-get-legs-amputated-for-1-3-million-insurance-scam-5281812%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22''4.5%20Hours%20Of%20Sleep''%3A%20X%20User%20Shares%20IIT-JEE%20Aspirant's%20Rigorous%20Schedule%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0IIT%20JEE%20(Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%E2%80%93%20Joint%20Entrance%20Exam)%20and%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20exam%20are%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20most%20prestigious%20exams%20in%20India%20and%20are%20attempted%20by%20lakhs%20of%20students%20across%20the%20country%20every%20year.%20The%20exams%20deemed%20to%20be%20the%20toughest%20in%20the%20country%20demand%20strategic%20planning%2C%20focused%20dedication%2C%20and%20a%20disciplined%20approach.%20Recently%2C%20a%20user%20on%20X%20shared%20the%20rigid%20schedule%20of%20a%20friend%20preparing%20for%20the%20JEE%20(Joint%20Entrance%20Examination)%2C%20underscoring%20the%20significance%20of%20time%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20user%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20name%20Mr.%20Rc%20on%20X%20and%20identifies%20himself%20as%20a%2016-year-old%2C%20shared%20a%20handwritten%20timetable%20of%20his%2017-year-old%20friend.%20''Schedule%20of%20a%20close%20friend%20who%20is%20preparing%20for%20JEE%2C''%20the%20caption%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20screenshot%20of%20the%20timetable%20outlined%20his%20daily%20activities%2C%20his%20sleep%20schedule%20and%20the%20time%20allocated%20to%20studies.%20The%20young%20aspirant%20gets%20up%20at%204%3A30%20am%20every%20day%2C%C2%A0after%20sleeping%20at%20midnight%2C%20getting%20just%204.5%20hours%20of%20sleep.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20day%20goes%20into%20revising%20old%20chapters%2C%20attending%20class%2C%20and%20completing%20class%20work%20and%20notes%20with%20hardly%20any%20time%20for%20leisure%20or%20other%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20picture%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F99hd5c8o_iit-jee-aspirant-schedule_625x300_21_March_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20motivate%20himself%2C%20the%20student%20also%20wrote%20an%20inspirational%20quote%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20schedule%20that%20read%2C%20''Never%20will%20you%20have%20this%20day%20again.%20So%20make%20it%20count.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20user%20who%20shared%20the%20post%20further%20said%20that%20his%20friend%20follows%20the%20timetable%20very%20precisely%20and%20is%20''filled%20with%20determination%20to%20bring%20his%20family%20out%20of%20poverty.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20his%20post%2C%20one%20user%20said%2C%20''Too%20hectic..no%20time%20for%20physical%20activity.''%20Another%20commented%2C%20''This%20looks%20good%2C%20especially%20those%20power-naps.%20Would%20request%20to%20begin%20the%20day%20with%20meditation%2Frunning%20and%20add%20any%20sports%20for%2030%20minutes%20later%20in%20the%20day.%20All%20the%20best.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20''Medical%20evidence%20shows%20that%20sleeping%20less%20than%207-8%20hours%20in%20teenage%20years%20leads%20to%20poor%20memory%2C%20lower%20learning%2C%20and%20atrophied%20problem-solving%20skills%20-%20everything%20teens%20need.%20Your%20friend%20should%20sleep%20more!''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20added%2C%20''that's%20some%20insane%20discipline%20if%20he%20does%20it%20consistently.%20My%20routine%20for%20NEET%20and%20JEE%20was%20very%20indisciplined%20and%20vague.%20Altho%20I%20had%20a%20decent%20success%2C%20but%20still%20I%20wish%20I%20was%20somewhat%20disciplined%20during%20prep%20time.%20may%20be%20it%20would%20have%20reduced%20some%20unnecessary%20stress.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20exam%20is%20divided%20into%20two%20levels%3A%20JEE%20Mains%20and%20JEE%20Advanced.%20Candidates%20have%20to%20first%20qualify%20for%20JEE%20Mains%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20advanced%20level%20of%20the%20entrance%20exam%20(JEE%20Advanced).%20The%20exam%20is%20held%20twice%20a%20year%20in%20office%20mode.%20The%20first%20exam%20is%20held%20in%20January%20and%20the%20second%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711007220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Feh0cjbo_iitjee-aspirants-schedule_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2F4-5-hours-of-sleep-x-user-shares-iit-jee-aspirants-rigid-daily-schedule-5281307%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20user%20on%20X%20shared%20the%20rigid%20schedule%20of%20a%20friend%20preparing%20for%20the%20JEE%20(Joint%20Entrance%20Examination).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2F4-5-hours-of-sleep-x-user-shares-iit-jee-aspirants-rigid-daily-schedule-5281307%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2F4-5-hours-of-sleep-x-user-shares-iit-jee-aspirants-rigid-daily-schedule-5281307%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2F4-5-hours-of-sleep-x-user-shares-iit-jee-aspirants-rigid-daily-schedule-5281307%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Rapper%20Badshah%20on%20New%20Album%20%E2%80%98Ek%20Tha%20Raja%2C%E2%80%99%20Working%20With%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20Arijit%20Singh%3A%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99m%20Like%20This%20Cousin%20Who%20Starts%20the%20Party%E2%80%99%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711006956000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBadshah.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235946960%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20rapper%2C%20singer-songwriter%20and%20music%20producer%20Badshah%20has%20just%20released%20his%20new%20album%20%E2%80%9CEk%20Tha%20Raja%E2%80%9D%20(literally%2C%20there%20was%20a%20king).%20It%20is%20the%20third%20studio%20album%20for%20the%20musician%20who%20w