%20the%20tribes%20through%20our%20initiatives%20to%20converge%20on%20dialogues%20that%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20Samvaad%20each%20year.%20Many%20new%20ideas%20and%20innovations%20emerge%20from%20these%20conversations%2C%20moderated%20by%20experts%20from%20respective%20fields%20and%20changemakers%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20Celebration%20of%20culture%20also%20forms%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20Samvaad%2C%20which%20not%20only%20generates%20livelihood%20for%20tribal%20artisans%20but%20also%20allows%20people%20to%20appreciate%20their%20unique%20traditions%2C%20passed%20down%20through%20generations%2C%20rich%20in%20wisdom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESamvaad%E2%80%99s%20varied%20ecosystem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magnitude%20of%20Samvaad%20is%20reflected%20in%20its%20diverse%20ecosystem%2C%20which%20includes%20promoting%20tribal%20healers%2C%20artisans%2C%20cuisines%2C%20languages%2C%20sports%20and%20heritage%20conservation%2C%20%3Cem%3EAkhra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ESamudaay%20ke%20Saath%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Rhythms%20of%20the%20Earth%2C%20Tribal%20Leadership%20Programme%2C%20Samvaad%20Fellowship%2C%20and%20Samvaad%20Action%20Research%20Collective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samvaad%20Fellowship%20aims%20to%20guide%20and%20nurture%20individuals%20committed%20to%20preserving%20tribal%20culture%20and%20heritage%20through%20community-based%20action.%20After%20a%20round%20of%20assessments%2C%20the%20fellows%20receive%20one-year%20grants%20and%20mentorships%20from%20academicians%20and%20experts.%20These%20fellowships%20have%20led%20to%20tangible%20outcomes%20like%20tribal%20dictionaries%2C%20song%20recordings%2C%20story%20books%20for%20children%2C%20collectives%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20contesting%20elections%20to%20making%20documentaries%20on%20tribal%20issues%2C%20many%20people%20have%20emerged%20as%20leaders%20and%20changemakers.%20Some%20have%20even%20failed.%20Irrespective%20of%20your%20failure%20or