aunched%20five%20original%20compositions%20on%20a%20tribal%20narrative%20at%20the%20conclave.%20The%20compositions%20are%20on%20the%20theme%20of%20unifying%20tribals%20in%20the%20face%20of%20adversity.%20They%20include%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENukhtharini%20Juwmang%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Rabha%20tribe%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EEklaivet%20Ajakong%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Karbi%20tribe%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EDela%20Dela%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Santal%20tribe%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAbua%20Disom%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20Ho%20tribe%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20outcome%20of%20Samvaad%E2%80%99s%20ten-year%20journey%20was%20seen%20in%20Jaincy%20John%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20to%20break%20away%20from%20the%20conventional%20narrative%20of%20urban%20education.%20Living%20in%20cities%20often%20limits%20our%20view%20of%20education%20to%20securing%20future%20jobs.%20However%2C%20for%20those%20in%20remote%20areas%20far%20from%20mainstream%20society%2C%20education%20is%20about%20identity%20and%20challenging%20stereotypes%20built%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20academician%20and%20activist%20from%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Mala%20Arya%20community%2C%20Jaincy%20challenged%20the%20stereotypes%20around%20tribal%20identity.%20While%20she%20was%20working%20on%20extensive%20pieces%20on%20Adivasi%20and%20Dalit%20art%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20history%2C%20and%20completing%20her%20PhD%2C%20she%20encountered%20discrimination%20and%20abuse%20from%20her%20guide.%20However%2C%20that%20did%20not%20deter%20her%20from%20her%20path.%20She%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20him%2C%20which%20further%20helped%20other%20women%20open%20up%20about%20their%20similar%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Jancy%20continues%20to%20fight%20the%20legal%20battle%2C%20Samvaad%20has%20supported%20the%20right%20of%20many%20tribal%20members%20to%20represent%20themselves%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22